@startuml
title Mapeamento C2 -> C3 (componentes vs. infra)

' Map logical containers to physical infra
package "Containers / Components (C2)" {
  [API Container] as API
  [DB Container] as DB
}
package "Physical/Infra (C3)" {
  [VM / Kubernetes] as Infra
  [SQL Database Service] as SQL
}

API -> Infra
DB -> SQL

@enduml